title: LF DuoQ (Around Plat 2 Elo)
body:
Kata/Ori/Lux main going for Diamond LF DuoQ preferably a jungler I guess.
Got 61% winrate on Katarina (95 Games) , 67% winrate on Orianna (18 games) , 63% winrate on Lux (24 Games) 
Secondary role ADC Vayne 54% winrate (26 Games)
Leave a comment and I'll add you, or just add me yourself : IGotJiminsJams on EUW, if interested.
